description:
This is a 32 minute workout called 'Low impact, high intensity intermediate home cardio workout' from the channel Body Project.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: https://teambodyproject.com

For more workouts like this, come and join us. New workouts weekly - over 300 workouts and multiple plans with the Body Project team. 

Turbo 20's is a challenging and fun 30 minute cardio workout. Low impact makes it great for the joints - but the workout is still challenging....
